values.name: title
values.description: .title { color: var(--baseColor); line-height: 1.5; font-family: var(--crm-font-regular); font-size: var(--crm-large-font-size); margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 400; }

values.name: darkSecHead
values.description: .darkSecHead { font-size: var(--crm-medium-font-size); padding-bottom: 10px; display: inline-block; color: var(--headingColor); font-family: var(--crm-font-bold) !important; }

values.name: dim4
values.description: .dim4 a:hover, .dim5 a:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: var(--0F5491); }

values.name: dim5
values.description: .dim4 a:hover, .dim5 a:hover { text-decoration: underline; color: var(--0F5491); }

values.name: elipse_toE
values.description: .elipse_toE, .ellipticText { text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; }

values.name: ellipticText
values.description: .elipse_toE, .ellipticText { text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; }

values.name: tbFreezelayer
values.description: .tbFreezelayer { opacity: 0.4; position: fixed; inset: 0px; z-index: 10; background: var(--bg_313949) !important; }

values.name: wFreezelayer
values.description: .wFreezelayer { background: var(--bg_white); opacity: 0.4; position: fixed; inset: 0px; z-index: 10; }

values.name: freezeLayer
values.description: .freezeLayer, .temp_freezelayer { position: fixed; inset: 0px; background: var(--bg_313949); opacity: 0.9; z-index: 20; width: 100% !important; height: auto !important; }

values.name: temp_freezelayer
values.description: .freezeLayer, .temp_freezelayer { position: fixed; inset: 0px; background: var(--bg_313949); opacity: 0.9; z-index: 20; width: 100% !important; height: auto !important; }

values.name: loading
values.description: .loading { background: url("/crm/images/zoho-busy.gif") no-repeat; width: 17px; height: 17px; opacity: 0.5; display: inline-block; }

values.name: hotlink
values.description: .hotlink { color: var(--f56d6d); font-size: var(--crm-small-font-size); white-space: nowrap; text-decoration: none; }

values.name: cfTabClass
values.description: .cfTabClass { padding: 20px 0px 0px; background-color: var(--bg_white); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--br_d7e2ed); }

values.name: newHelpLinkIcon
values.description: .newHelpLinkIcon { color: var(--labelColor); position: relative; padding-right: 22px; vertical-align: top; }

values.name: newHelpLinkIcon
values.description: .newHelpLinkIcon::before { content: ""; position: absolute; background-image: var(--crmLyteSprite); background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: -388px -689px; width: 15px; height: 17px; opacity: 0.8; top: calc(50% - 9px); right: 0px; }

values.name: infoCont
values.description: .infoCont { background: var(--infoBgColor); border: 1px solid var(--infoBrColor); color: var(--baseColor); border-radius: 6px; }

values.name: noteinfocont
values.description: .noteinfocont { border: 1px solid var(--noteBrColor); color: var(--noteColor); border-radius: 6px; background: var(--noteBgColor); }

values.name: warninginfocont
values.description: .warninginfocont { border: 1px solid var(--orangeLightBr); color: var(--baseColor); border-radius: 6px; background: var(--orangeLightBg); }

values.name: tagCont
values.description: .tagCont { border: 1px solid var(--br_d9e8f9); border-radius: 4px; background: var(--bg_e7f2ff) !important; color: var(--baseColor) !important; }

values.name: darkMainHead
values.description: .darkMainHead { font-size: var(--crm-large-font-size); color: var(--headingColor); line-height: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: var(--crm-font-bold) !important; }

values.name: bor
values.description: .bor { border-top-color: ; border-top-style: ; border-top-width: ; border-right-color: ; border-right-style: ; border-right-width: ; border-bottom-color: ; border-bottom-style: ; border-bottom-width: ; border-image-source: ; border-image-slice: ; border-image-width: ; border-image-outset: ; border-image-repeat: ; border-left: 0px; }

values.name: bT1B1
values.description: .bT1B1 { border-top: 1px solid var(--br_c0c6cc) !important; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--br_c0c6cc) !important; }

values.name: mW188
values.description: .mW188 { max-width: 188px; text-overflow: ellipsis; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; }

values.name: mw140
values.description: .mw140 { max-width: 140px; text-overflow: ellipsis; overflow: hidden; display: inline-block; white-space: nowrap; vertical-align: bottom; }

values.name: mw150
values.description: .mw150 { max-width: 150px; text-overflow: ellipsis; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-block; }

values.name: mw250

values.name: mw228

values.name: mw130
values.description: .mw130 { max-width: 130px; text-overflow: ellipsis; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-block; }

values.name: mw110
values.description: .mw110 { max-width: 110px; text-overflow: ellipsis; overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; display: inline-block; }
